        ]]></sql>
        <!-- Empty (#1368 migration-correctness fix): same reasoning as changeset -13's rollback — once a
             config_audit_event row carries WORKSPACE_LLM_CONNECTION or WORKSPACE_LLM_MODEL, re-adding the
             narrower CHECK is a data-preserving downgrade that does not exist (the audit trail is
